        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: WebChat stop fails for WeChat channel sessions",
        "body": "Related: #91987\n\n## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes WebChat `/stop` failing to stop looping channel-originated agent turns, observed with a WeChat channel session selected in WebChat.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nWebChat exact stop text now bypasses slash-menu selection and is submitted as the typed command, so `/stop` reliably reaches the abort path.\n\nThe gateway abort path now preserves the selected explicit channel session key across the active state used by this flow:\n\n- `chatAbortControllers` for normal WebChat/chat runs\n- hidden registered or pre-registered channel runs when the request names that explicit channel session\n- `replyRunRegistry` for active channel auto-reply operations that do not have a chat abort controller\n\nBroad `agent:main`/global stop requests no longer infer a hidden channel session. They abort only matching visible/global scope unless the request already carries the explicit channel session key.\n\n## User Impact\n\nUsers viewing a WeChat/channel session in WebChat can stop a looping channel agent with `/stop`. Broad visible sessions still do not accidentally stop unrelated hidden channel work.\n\n## Evidence\n\nVideo proof:\n\n- Before fix:\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1107f4e1-8450-4f2b-981a-ac5815673ed2\n\n- After fix:\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/25f32135-1f1a-4f9c-b0a7-ddade5464b86\n\nAutomated/local proof:\n\n- Manual local proof: rebuilt gateway/Control UI, restarted local gateway, reproduced WeChat channel loop, and confirmed WebChat `/stop` stopped the running turn.\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-chat.test.ts src/gateway/server-methods/chat.abort-persistence.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs src/gateway/server-methods/chat.ts src/gateway/server-methods/chat.abort-persistence.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-chat.ts ui/src/ui/app-chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm tsgo:core`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n",
        "branch": "fix-webchat-stop-hidden-channel-runs",
